CREATE TYPE zone_action AS ENUM ('ShowGPS', 'ShowText', 'Hide');
ALTER TABLE zonenames ADD COLUMN action zone_action;
ALTER TABLE zonenames ADD COLUMN text varchar(255);
	
HARDCODED CONFIGURATION

The file gogodex.tac has the location of the backend module hardcoded in.
This is necessary because you do not run this using the python command but
using the twistd command, which is located somewhere else. Change this file
location appropriatly.

The top __init__ function in backend.py specifies the database name, username,
and user password for the postgres. Change that appropriatly.

Optional: If you want to change the port this runs on, change it in gogodex.tac
Default is port 79, for no reason.
